## Limitations

The findings are based on available data and may not capture the full spectrum of voter preferences, especially in rapidly changing political environments. Additionally, the emphasis on certain qualities can vary significantly depending on the socio-political context and the specific challenges faced by the nation at any given time. The data is also limited to the sources accessed, which may not represent all demographic groups equally.